      "text": "Quest: Help each of the Chanthros fix their equipment so the party can continue.\n\nOnce complete, the head Chanthro will reward you with a dressing room pass, after which you can open a vent and get to the [[Music Nerd]] boss arena, a secret dance floor only known to VIPs in his crime organization (his close friends).",
