      "x": -1520,
      "y": -3572
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 100,
      "id": "501d8d37010e0ff6",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Player is kidnapped by thugs and rescued by [[Chandroid]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 400,
      "x": -2360,
      "y": -4300
    },
    {
      "height": 107,
      "id": "648c07aeade4a558",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "player explores city, finding [[Maid Factory]] and lowering bridge leading to boss",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 534,
      "x": -3442,
      "y": -3740
    },
    {
      "height": 440,
      "id": "7794badbd8e89e23",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Quest: Buoys block the way to the boss.\n\nDock workers saw shipments of batteries going to the island, but they were suspicious of them.\n\nGet a boat running to sail to the buoys, allowing you to jump over them.\n\nTo get the boat, enter [[Chandroid]] into the [[Baddest Babe on the Beach Contest]], and win.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 610,
      "x": -2000,
      "y": -3090
    },
