    },
    {
      "height": 240,
      "id": "fe8b11fcc89cd064",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Island has abandoned laboratory, previously used by [[Science Nerd]].\n[[Octopus]] and buoys are used by him to keep prying eyes away from the evidence",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 460,
      "x": -1360,
      "y": -3040
    },
    {
      "color": "6",
      "height": 60,
      "id": "2c96d3a04344f67f",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Internet",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": -1950,
      "y": -2480
    },
    {
      "height": 1300,
      "id": "1c11ab79195b7f5b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### Ch. 1\nOpening---[[DnD Nerd]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Inspector Specs]]\n[[Quantum Traveling Device]]\n[[Metal Boots]]\n[[Rewire]]\n[[Bouncy Skirt]]\n\n### Ch. 2--A\nHighway---Blocked Suburb Entrance (rocks)\n\nRequires:\n[[Shoulder Upgrade]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Floaties]]\n\n### Ch. 2--B\nSewer---[[Tech Nerd]]\n\nRequires:\n[[Floaties]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Shoulder Upgrade]]\n\n### Ch. 3\nSuburbs---[[Fangirl Nerd]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1350,
      "x": -80,
      "y": -3540
    },
